data.description: This is a great little 3/2, with an office, in the heart of Cleveland.  Outside you'll find the house sits on three lots, so there's plenty of room to spread out. The yard is one of the biggest in that area. There is a detached 2-car garage/workshop with an apartment attached. The apartment is also equipped with a kitchenette. Inside you'll find a classic '70s floorplan with wood and tile floors, large rooms, and nice flow. There is so much potential in this home. This could be an amazing find with a bit of sweat equity! Really neat house. Lot next door is available for sale also if you want an even bigger yard.
